  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK917">
<l>niṟaineñca millavar tōyvar piṟaneñciṟ</l>
<l>pēṇip puṇarpavar tōḷ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who are destitute of a perfectly (reformed) mind will covet the shoulders of those who embrace (them) while their hearts covet other things.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
